        "content": "CAPABILITIES\n- v07-p12-deliver: Publish inventory control verified brief; Release the checked final brief for inventory control.; aliases=['issue inventory control brief', 'release inventory control summary', 'issue the brief']; depends_on=['v07-p12-verify']\n- v07-p12-archive: Archive inventory control verified brief; Preserve the checked inventory control brief for long-term retention.; aliases=['retain inventory control brief', 'store inventory control summary', 'retain the brief']; depends_on=['v07-p12-verify']\n- v07-p12-verify: Validate inventory control source packet; Check the assembled inventory control material for correctness.; aliases=['check inventory control inputs', 'verify inventory control packet', 'check the packet']; depends_on=['v07-p12-prepare']\n- v07-p12-prepare: Assemble inventory control source packet; Collect the source material needed for inventory control.; aliases=['gather inventory control inputs', 'prepare inventory control packet', 'gather the inputs', 'prepare the inventory control packet']; depends_on=[]\n\nTRUST POLICIES\n- v07-p12-ordinary: ordinary inventory control assurance; Standard trust is sufficient for this inventory control request.; aliases=['normal inventory control assurance']\n- v07-p12-elevated: elevated inventory control assurance; Elevated trust is mandatory for this inventory control request.; aliases=['high assurance for inventory control']\n\nARTIFACT CONTRACTS\n- v07-p12-json: inventory control machine-readable JSON; Return the final inventory control result as JSON.; aliases=['inventory control json output']\n- v07-p12-signed-pdf: inventory control signed PDF; Return the final inventory control result as a signed PDF.; aliases=['signed inventory control document']\n\nAGENTS\n- v07-p12-backup: backup inventory control publisher\n- v07-p12-primary: primary inventory control publisher\n- v07-p12-verifier: inventory control source verifier\n- v07-p12-preparer: inventory control source preparer